Requirements
1. Any logitech mouse that is supported by Logitech GHUB 
2. Logitech GHUB 
3. Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six Siege 
4. If you have an IQ under 100 then read the clear instructions in the lua.
_____________________________________________________________________________
Instructions
1.open ghub-
2.click profiles
3.add a new rainbow six siege profile (if you dont have a r6 profile click on add a application and find the pathway for r6) 
4.when you have the profile click on add a script 
5.then click add a lua scirpt then copy the lua and save&close 
6.done
